<ol class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-neutral-700">
  <li class="grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-x-4">
    <span class="text-emerald-700 tabular-nums">01</span>
    <div>
      <p class="text-neutral-900">Open your repo's <strong class="font-medium">Settings &raquo; Webhooks &raquo; Add webhook</strong>.</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-neutral-500">Webhooks are per-repo. For all-repo coverage, add one at the org level under <strong class="font-medium">Organization settings &raquo; Webhooks</strong>.</p>
    </div>
  </li>
  <li class="grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-x-4">
    <span class="text-emerald-700 tabular-nums">02</span>
    <div class="min-w-0">
      <p class="text-neutral-900">Paste this Payload URL and set Content type to <code class="text-neutral-700">application/json</code>.</p>
      <%= render "webhook_url_field", url: public_webhook_url(parser_type: source.parser_type, token: source.token) %>
    </div>
  </li>
  <li class="grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-x-4">
    <span class="text-emerald-700 tabular-nums">03</span>
    <div>
      <p class="text-neutral-900">Pick <strong class="font-medium">Let me select individual events</strong> and check the ones that matter:</p>
      <ul role="list" class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-xs text-neutral-500">
        <li><code class="text-neutral-700">Issues</code> — only new issues notify</li>
        <li><code class="text-neutral-700">Issue comments</code> — new comments on issues</li>
        <li><code class="text-neutral-700">Workflow runs</code> — only failed runs notify</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </li>
  <li class="grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-x-4">
    <span class="text-emerald-700 tabular-nums">04</span>
    <div class="min-w-0">
      <p class="text-neutral-900">Copy this signing secret and paste it into GitHub's Secret field.</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-neutral-500">GitHub signs each request with HMAC-SHA256 using this secret.</p>
      <%= render "signing_secret_field", source: source %>
    </div>
  </li>
</ol>
